Title: Chrysler Delta alloy wheel bolts M12 x 1.25 taper 17mm Hex set of 16
Description:
This listing is for a set of 16 brand new wheel bolts.

These nuts are top quality high tensile carbon steel which is bright zinc plated to resist rust.

Suitable for original and after market wheels.



 Specifications
Thread size: M12 x 1.25
Thread length: 26mm
Overall bolt width: 23mm
Overall bolt length: 51mm (inc the head)
Seat type: Tapered (Cone shaped)
Bolt material: Heat treated carbon alloy steel
Bolt finish: Bright zinc plated
Spanner size: 17mm Hex
 
 

 

 




FAQ's
Below are some of the common questions we get with some answers

What is Hex?
The Hex refers to the size of the nut/bolt head and therefore the corresponding size of the socket used with the wheel brace.

What is the seat?
The seat is the part of the nut/bolt that comes into contact with the wheel in the bolt holes.
There are 3 main styles of seat
Tapered - usually 60 degrees, this looks like a cone
Radius - this looks like a bowl
Flat - this is usually a flat washer.

What is M12 x 1.25?
This is the size of the thread.
The M number is the diameter of the thread and the 1.25 is the size of the pitch between each individual threads.
So an M12 x 1.25 is a 12mm diameter by 1.25mm thread.



There are 4 common sizes
M12 x1.25
M12 x 1.5
M14 x 1.25
M14 x 1.5

How do I know what nuts or bolts I need?
We have tried to make it as easy as possible for you to identify the correct nuts/bolts for your car.
If the compatibility info of this listing is states for your car then this will be the standard fitment you require.
If you are still not sure please feel free to call us on 01622 735368 and a member of our team will be happy to help.
